To start building a react project you must USE 

1
	npx  create-react-app  YOUR-name

2
	updagrade package.json dependencies key with everything in 
	https://gist.github.com/gwmccubbin/fb80787126657d3274584ffb3d415650

3 
	install hardhat  >> npx hardhat 


4
	initialize Hardhat >> npx hardhat node
	
5 
	when creating contracts we need to specify hardhat.config.js values

	networks: {localHost: {url: "OUR LOCAL URL SHOWN IN >> npx hardhat node"}}

6
	COMPILE
		>> npx hardhat compile

7  HARDHAT run scripts
	>> npx hardhat run --network localhost ./scripts/1_deploy.js

8 HARDHAT CONSOLE
	>> npx hardhat console --network localhost




